sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Premium User
    participant FE as React<br/>PacketInspectorPage
    participant WS as Django Channels<br/>PacketConsumer
    participant Task as capture_packets_task
    participant Extractor as PacketFeatureExtractor

    FE->>WS: WebSocket CONNECT ws/packets/
    WS->>WS: connect() → group_add("packets")
    WS-->>FE: Connection established
    Note over Task: Background capture running
    Task->>Extractor: extract(packet)
    Extractor->>Extractor: _calculate_port_entropy()
    Extractor-->>Task: Feature dict (protocol, flags, payload_size, ...)
    Task->>WS: channel_layer.group_send("packets", packet_data)
    WS->>WS: packet_message(event)
    WS-->>FE: JSON {src_ip, dst_ip, protocol, flags, payload_size, ...}
    FE->>FE: getProtocolColor(protocol)
    FE->>FE: PacketDetail(packet) panel
    FE-->>U: Render live packet stream with detail inspector
